      "text": "Hey there.  While you _can_ you Select-String, you can also use this module I made for Subtitles\n\ngithub.com/StartAutomat...\n\nShould be something like:\n\nGet-Subtitle $pathToSubtitles | Search-Subtitle -Phrase $phraseToSearch\n\nWill spit back out StartTime, EndTime, and Cue."
